            You can easily plug in your current funds, accounts, and debts to see where you stand, or plug in hypothetical data so you know what to expect when you want to set financial goals for yourself. This can serve as a reference point to see how much you need to save, or how much debt you can afford to have. This calculation is at the root of everyone's financial strategy, whether they consider it thoughtfully or not. 
